    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Jet Fighters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Alerted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SAN FRANCISCO, July [unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "— Military aircraft hunted the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "skies over Pacific Coast states",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "today for sight of the mysterious",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "\"flying saucers\" that for 12 days",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "have puzzled the entire country.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Early reports of results were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "negative.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Five P-51s of the Oregon Na-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "tional Guard cruised over the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Cascade Mountains of Washing-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "ton—the area where the strange",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "objects first were reported sight-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "ed. A sixth circled over Portland,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "in constant radio contact with the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "other five. All carried photo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "graphic equipment.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Col. G. R. Dodson, command-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "ing, described their flight as a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "\"routine patrol,\" but said they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "had been instructed to watch for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "At Manhattan Beach, Calif., A.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "W. McKelvey took a Mustang",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "fighter plane up above Van Nuys.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "For two hours he cruised at 35,-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "000 feet, but \"didn't see a thing.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Gen. Carl Spaatz, commandant",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of the Army Air Forces, was on a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Pacific Northwest fishing trip.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "He denied knowing anything",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "about the flying discs — or of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "plans to use AAF planes to look",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "for them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "JET FIGHTER SET",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "\"I've been out of touch with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "things for four or five days,\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Louis E. Starr, national com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "mander-in-chief of the Veterans",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "of Foreign Wars, yesterday in Co-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "lumbus, O., said he understood",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Spaatz had a \"group out right",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "now\" looking for discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "At Muroc Army Air Field in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "California a P-80 jet fighter stood",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "ready to take off the moment any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "flying saucers are sighted in that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "area.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "A cautious attitude marked",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "both official and scientific com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "ments, but Capt. Tom Brown of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "the Air Forces Public Relations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "staff in Washington acknowl-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "edged the Air Forces had decided",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "\"there's something to this\" and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "had been checking up on it for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "12 days.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "SEEN IN 36 STATES",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "First sighted June 25 and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "greeted generally with scornful",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "laughs, the objects have been re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "ported every day since by observ-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "ers in 36 states. Most of the ob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "jects were reported seen July 4.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "A few were reported yesterday.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "Such competent observers as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "airline pilots said they had seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "the totally unexplained discs or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "saucers, larger than aircraft and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "flying in \"loose formation\" at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "high speed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "David Lilienthal, chairman of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "the Atomic Energy Commission,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "said they had nothing to do with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "atomic experiments, and Army",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "and Navy officials also entered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "positive disclaimers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "Newspaper stories quoting an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "unidentified California Institute",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "of Technology scientist as saying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "the phenomena might have some-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "thing to do with experiments in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "\"transmutation of atomic energy\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "caused a brief sensation late yes-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "terday. The institute quickly de-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "nied the report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "Reports generally agreed that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "the flying objects were round or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "oval. Estimates of their speed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "ranged from about 300 to 1,200",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "miles an hour. They were de-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "scribed as flying with an undu-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "lating motion at heights of 10,000",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "feet and less. Some described",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "them as glowing, or luminous.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "PROPELLER IN CENTER",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "Nova Hart, St. Louis mechanic",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "who was trained during service",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "in the war to spot all types of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "aircraft, said he saw one of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "strang objects near Pattonville",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "yesterday. It was flying at 300",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "feet, he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "He described it as circular, with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "a ribbed framework and silver",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "gray in color. Hart said it ap-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "peared to have a motor with a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "propeller attached in the center",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "and it kept turning like an air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "plane doing a slow roll.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "First published reports of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "phenomena occurred June 25.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "Kenneth Arnold, Boise, Ida.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "businessman pilot, told of seeing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "nine of the discs flying in forma-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "tion at 1,200 miles an hour over",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "the Cascade Mountains in Wash-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "ington.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "SEEN BY 200",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "Arnold's account was taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "lightly. Various explanations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "were offered—\"reflections,\" \"per-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "sistent vision,\" \"snow blindness.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "Soon afterward other individ-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "uals—in New Mexico, Missouri,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "California and other states—re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "ported they also had seen the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "text": "flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "text": "Then on Independence Day 200",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "text": "persons in one group and 60 in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "text": "another saw them in Idaho. Hun-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "text": "dreds of others in Oregon, Wash-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "text": "ington and other western states",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "text": "reported seeing them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "text": "July 4 also brought first re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 150,
      "text": "ports of the flying discs from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "text": "east of the Mississippi. Since",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "text": "then they have been reported seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "text": "in widely separated sections of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "text": "the country—in 33 states in all.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 156,
      "text": "'Must Be Insane'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "text": "LONDON, July 6—(AP)—Don't",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "text": "mention those flying saucers on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "text": "this side of the Atlantic unless",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "text": "you're prepared for an argument",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "text": "about your sanity.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "text": "Maybe they have been seen by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "text": "sober citizens over a vast area",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "text": "of the United States, but Europe",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 166,
      "text": "won't believe in them until some-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 167,
      "text": "body lassoes one and has it photo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 168,
      "text": "graphed by Frank Sinatra, the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 169,
      "text": "British ambassador and five",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 170,
      "text": "Supreme Court justices.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 171,
      "text": "\"America's reply to the Loch",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 172,
      "text": "Ness monster,\" chortled today's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 173,
      "text": "Sunday dispatch, referring to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 174,
      "text": "Britain's hoariest tall story—the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "text": "serpent that is \"seen\" romping in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 176,
      "text": "Scotland's Loch Ness every time",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
